    <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--text)]">
      This page explains what melanotan is and why it acts as it does. It does not
      provide dosing, sourcing, or usage instructions, and it is not medical
      advice or an endorsement of an unapproved product. If you are worried about a
      mole or a reaction, see a clinician. See the
      <a href="/about">editorial standards</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

